<!-- ============================================================
     LOCAL SEO PARAGRAPH
     ============================================================ -->
{%- if section.settings.local_seo_paragraph != blank -%}
<div class="city-about">
  <h2>Custom Trophy Makers in {{ city }}, {{ city_state }}</h2>
  {%- capture rm_city_content -%}
    {{ section.settings.local_seo_paragraph }}
  {%- endcapture -%}
  {%- render 'read-more-wrapper',
    content: rm_city_content,
    id: 'city-seo-readmore',
    collapsed_height: 220
  -%}
</div>
{%- endif -%}

<!-- ============================================================
     FEATURED PRODUCTS
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="city-products">
  <h2 class="city-section-title">Trophies &amp; Awards — Popular Picks</h2>
  <div class="city-products__grid">
    {%- for product in collections.all.products limit: 8 -%}
      <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="city-product-card">
        {%- if product.featured_image -%}
          <img
            class="city-product-card__img"
            src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 400 }}"
            alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape | default: product.title | escape }}"
            width="400"
            height="400"
            loading="lazy"
          >
        {%- else -%}
          <div class="city-product-card__img" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#aaa;font-size:0.8rem;">No image</div>
        {%- endif -%}
        <div class="city-product-card__body">
          <div class="city-product-card__title">{{ product.title | escape }}</div>
          <div class="city-product-card__price">
            {{ product.price | money }}
            {%- if product.compare_at_price > product.price -%}
              <s>{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</s>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     DELIVERY COVERAGE
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="city-delivery">
  <div class="city-delivery__inner">
    <h2 class="city-section-title" style="text-align:left;margin-bottom:8px;">Trophy Delivery Coverage in {{ city }}</h2>
    <p style="color:#555;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.6;">
      We deliver trophies, medals, and corporate gifts to all major areas across {{ city }}.
      Order online and receive your customised awards at your doorstep — typically within 3–7 business days.
    </p>
    {%- assign areas = delivery_areas | split: "," -%}
    <div class="city-delivery__areas">
      {%- for area in areas -%}
        <span class="city-delivery__tag">{{ area | strip }}</span>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     FAQ — VISIBLE HTML
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="city-faq" id="faq">
  <div class="city-faq__inner">
    <h2 class="city-section-title" style="text-align:left;">Frequently Asked Questions — Trophies in {{ city }}</h2>
    <p style="color:#555;font-size:0.93rem;margin-bottom:4px;">Everything you need to know about ordering custom trophies, medals, and awards in {{ city }}.</p>

    <div class="city-faq__list">

      <div class="city-faq__item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <button class="city-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
          <span itemprop="name">Where can I buy custom trophies in {{ city }}?</span>
          <span class="city-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="city-faq__a" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <div itemprop="text">
            You can order custom trophies in {{ city }} directly from Meru Trophy at <strong>merutrophy.in</strong>. We are a Bangalore-based trophy manufacturer with over 20 years of experience, and we deliver Pan India including all areas in {{ city }}. Browse our full collection online, customise your order, and we'll deliver to your doorstep. You can also call us at +91 7892207252 or WhatsApp +91 9480150888 to discuss bulk or corporate orders.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-faq__item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <button class="city-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
          <span itemprop="name">What is the price of a custom trophy in {{ city }}?</span>
          <span class="city-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="city-faq__a" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <div itemprop="text">
            Trophy prices in {{ city }} at Meru Trophy start from as low as ₹150 for simple medals and go up to ₹5,000+ for premium crystal or metal trophies with custom engraving. Factors that affect the price include the material (crystal, metal, acrylic, fibre, wood), size, engraving complexity, and quantity. Bulk orders of 50 or more pieces qualify for special discounted pricing. Contact us for a quote tailored to your event and budget.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-faq__item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <button class="city-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
          <span itemprop="name">How long does trophy delivery take in {{ city }}?</span>
          <span class="city-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="city-faq__a" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <div itemprop="text">
            Standard delivery to {{ city }} takes 3–7 business days after your order is confirmed and artwork is approved. For urgent requirements — such as a sports event or corporate function — we offer expedited production. Please WhatsApp us at +91 9480150888 with your event date, quantity, and design requirements so we can confirm the fastest possible turnaround for your location in {{ city }}.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-faq__item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <button class="city-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
          <span itemprop="name">Can I get engraving on trophies ordered from {{ city }}?</span>
          <span class="city-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="city-faq__a" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <div itemprop="text">
            Yes. All trophies, medals, shields, and plaques ordered through Meru Trophy can be engraved with recipient names, event titles, dates, serial numbers, or your company logo. We support laser engraving and UV printing on crystal, metal, acrylic, and wooden mementos. Simply provide the text or artwork file (JPG, PNG, or PDF) when placing your order, and our design team will share a proof before production begins.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-faq__item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <button class="city-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
          <span itemprop="name">What types of trophies are available for delivery in {{ city }}?</span>
          <span class="city-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="city-faq__a" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <div itemprop="text">
            Meru Trophy ships the following award categories to {{ city }}: Crystal Trophies, Metal Trophies, Fibre Trophies, Acrylic Trophies, Wooden Mementos, Medals, Shields, Plaques, and Corporate Gifts. Whether you need awards for a school sports day, cricket tournament, corporate recognition ceremony, employee of the month, or farewell event, we have a product to suit every occasion and budget.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-faq__item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <button class="city-faq__q" aria-expanded="false">
          <span itemprop="name">Does Meru Trophy accept bulk trophy orders for events in {{ city }}?</span>
          <span class="city-faq__q-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="city-faq__a" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <div itemprop="text">
            Absolutely. Bulk orders are our specialty. We regularly fulfill orders of 50 to 5,000+ pieces for corporate award nights, school annual days, marathons, cricket tournaments, and government events across {{ city_state }}. Bulk customers in {{ city }} receive volume discounts, dedicated account support, and consistent quality across every piece. WhatsApp us at +91 9480150888 with your quantity and event date to get a bulk quote within a few hours.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-faq__item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
